data.description: Did you ever wonder what a difference 4 feet would make?  When these original owners had this home built, they added 4' to the west side of the home which added this EXTRA footage to the garage, kitchen/laundry & guest bedrooms, allowing EXTRA space for rooms, closets & storage!  This means EXTRA space you'll truly appreciate along with the perfect location on a dead end/culdesac street just minutes to the nearby Rainbow River & park with its natural waterfalls & swimming/kayaking in the clear blue Rainbow Springs!  Indulge yourself by daydreaming, entertaining or just relaxing on your 10'x39' screened-in lanai with its gorgeous, private back yard view of the community-owned DRA(Drainage Retention Area, promising you NO neighbors in your back yard!). The home's split floor plan & pocket door on the guest side will give your family/friends added privacy & comfort they'll appreciate!  Enjoy the included lawn maintenance so you'll have more time to enjoy your Florida lifestyle!  This community has exclusive access to the boat/kayak launch, swimming area, covered picnic & grilling area to the river! Access Rails-to-Trails, nearby, for biking/hiking enthusiasts!  Check out the video and/or make an appointment to see this Fox Trace gem today!
